up.stateIntro: Uttar Pradesh is a state in northern India. With over 200 million inhabitants, it is the most populated state in India as well as the most populous country subdivision in the world.

2017: Samajwadi Party (SP) + Rashtriya Lok Dal (RLD) + Suheldev Bharatiya Samaj Party (SBSP) + Mahan Dal + Janvadi Party (Socialist)
